The OCF lab is located on the ground level of Hearst Gym (west entrance), Room 6A. You will need to show your student ID when you pass the Publications Center in Room 6.

[<img src="http://www.ocf.berkeley.edu/map_hearst.png" alt="OCF lab map" width="400px" height="191px">](http://ocfblog.blogspot.com/2012/06/moving-to-hearst-gym.html)

The lab is officially open during the Publications Center hours, currently (during fall/spring semesters):

* Weekdays: 9 AM to 6 PM
* Saturdays: 11 AM to 6 PM
* Sundays:  12 PM to 5 PM

OCF staff members are **not present** during all of these hours.

OCF staff members will be in the lab during the listed [staff hours](http://www.ocf.berkeley.edu/staff_hours), and intermittently at other times.
